**Template E — Big Audit (Auto-Split):**
```
Spawn main audit agent
⏳ Wait 3 min
Check: running >3min? Has independent parts?
  YES → Split!
    Agent A: modules A-C (300s)
    Agent B: modules D-F (300s)
    Agent C: modules G-K (300s)
  NO → Let finish (900s)
After ALL complete → Merge findings → Report to Boss
```

